            "summary": "Sunil Rohatgi, MD, a board-certified medical oncologist and hematologist, has joined Florida Cancer Specialists & Research Institute, LLC (FCS) in Citrus County. He will be offering his expertise in cancer treatment to patients in the area. This addition strengthens the team of cancer specialists at FCS, further enhancing the quality of care provided to the community. Dr. Rohatgi's presence underscores FCS's commitment to improving healthcare services for cancer patients in Florida.",
